_sText:
surf_tuscany_go | new surf map by Exxe

This is my 3rd approach to surf-mapping. 
It's a T2 staged map with 8 stages and 4 bonuses.

B1 by Trickster
B2 by Edy
B3 by Exxe
B4 by Taiikii

Showcase surfed by Taiikii.

Testers:
Edy
Granis
Watti
Taiikii
Pozy
Seras
Sneaky

Credits:
Skybox by Karatekaefer
Textures by: Tophatwaffle, Valve
Models: Trees by DomiTibingen, 3d open source models

Enjoy surfing + for troubleshooting pls hook me up on dc

Edit 05.08.21 : Fixed an Xploit on Stage 8 where ppl could jump over the walls towards the stage end. 
Fixed the solidity of 2 stones on S8 end where ppl could bhop in the endzone.
